<TEXT>
<P>
 Police have identified the body of a man found Thursday by a county work crew 
as Carlos Huerta Villavicencio, 28, of San Clemente. 
</P>
<P>
 Villavicencio had been shot several times in the upper torso with a 
small-caliber gun, according to Orange County Sheriff's Lt. Dan Martini. The 
