<HEADLINE>
<P>
CITY SECTION FOOTBALL ROUNDUP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By ERIC BARAD 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Cleveland 33, Poly 14 -- Running back Chuma Lewis rushed for 91 yards in eight 
carries and scored two touchdowns to lead the Cavaliers at Poly. 
</P>
<P>
 The Cavaliers rushed for 204 yards and amassed 281 yards in offense. 
</P>
<P>
 Damon Williams rushed for 77 yards in 12 carries. 
</P>
<P>
 Poly was led by quarterback Ricardo Gamboa, who completed 12 of 26 passes for 
156 yards. Gamboa was sacked five times. 
</P>
<P>
 Leaford Hacket of Poly caught six passes for 113 yards. 
</P>
<P>
 Cleveland built leads of 21-0 and 33-6, and had 20 first downs to Poly's 
eight. ERIC BARAD 
</P>
