<TEXT>
<P>
 Van Nuys 31, Palisades 13 -- Running back Larry Reed rushed for 170 yards in 
18 carries and scored four touchdowns to lead Van Nuys at Palisades. 
</P>
<P>
 He also caught three passes for 43 yards. Reed scored on runs of four, three, 
11 and 23 yards. 
</P>
<P>
 Van Nuys took a 14-6 lead on Reed's first two touchdowns. 
</P>
<P>
 Van Nuys kicker Arroyo Frederico connected on a 44-yard field goal for the 
Wolves on the last play of the first half for a 17-6 lead. 
</P>
<P>
 Van Nuys quarterback Chris Byfield completed seven of 12 for 95 yards and a 
touchdown. TODD JACOBSON 
