<TEXT>
<P>
 Chatsworth 21, Reseda 10 -- Quarterback Aaron Hummel completed 18 of 28 passes 
for 281 yards and two touchdowns to rally Chatsworth from a 10-7 halftime 
deficit at Reseda. 
</P>
<P>
 Hummel threw for 251 yards in the second half and connected with Brian 
