<TEXT>
<P>
 St. Joseph 35, Santa Clara 0 -- Ali Azziz rushed for 168 yards in 17 carries 
and scored four touchdowns to lead St. Joseph to a romp over Santa Clara at St. 
Joseph. 
</P>
<P>
 The overwhelmed Saints were limited to 102 total yards, including only 34 in 
the first half. St. Joseph led, 28-0, at halftime. 
</P>
<P>
 Azziz piled up 127 yards and three touchdowns by halftime and came out of the 
game midway through the third quarter after his fourth score. 
</P>
<P>
 His touchdowns came on runs of 11, 10, 15, and 28 yards. CAM INMAN 
