<HEADLINE>
<P>
SOUTHERN SECTION FOOTBALL ROUNDUP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By MIKE YEAMAN 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Royal 23, Oxnard 14 -- Tailback Mike Reddington rushed for 143 yards and 
sparked a second-half rally with a one-yard run in the third quarter to lead 
Royal at Oxnard. 
</P>
<P>
 After Reddington's touchdown gave Royal a 9-7 lead, the Highlanders scored 
again in the third quarter on a 17-yard pass from Wes Lagatta to Jerome Lee to 
increase their lead to 16-7.Lagatta completed eight of 12 passes for 137 yards. 
</P>
<P>
 Oxnard led, 7-0, in the first quarter after quarterback Taj Lewis scored on a 
46-yard run. Lewis completed 12 of 28 for 124 yards, including a three-yard 
scoring pass to Tim Ordenoz with 30 seconds to play. Lewis rushed for 130 yards 
in 18 carries. 
</P>
<P>
 Royal receiver Jermaine Smith had three receptions for 41 yards and teammate 
Jerome Lee had three catches for 38 yards. 
</P>
<P>
 For Oxnard, Arthur Jenkins caught four passes for 49 yards and teammate 
Richard Arguelles had three receptions for 27 yards. Arguelles had 84 yards in 
four carries. MIKE YEAMAN 
