 Esperanza 21, Sunny Hills 6 -- Mike Stanley and John Zinn had four goals each 
for visiting Esperanza in the season opener for both teams. 
</P>
<P>
 Santa Ana 19, Loara 17 -- Edgar Perez had nine goals and Luis Perez had seven 
goals to lead Santa Ana (1-0). Micheal Timanus had eight goals for Loara (0-1). 
</P>
<P>
 Tustin 16, Long Beach Millikan 2 -- David Foley and Marshall Bauernfiend each 
scored four goals for visiting Tustin. 
