<HEADLINE>
<P>
O.C. RELIGION NOTES / DAYE CLARK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By DAYE CLARK 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Lutheran Church of the Resurrection in Huntington Beach will install the Rev. 
E. Carl Zimmerman as senior pastor Sunday at 5 p.m. The Rev. Daniel Erlenbusch 
will give the sermon, and Bishop Robert L. Miller of the Pacifica Synod will 
conduct the installation. 
</P>
<P>
 Zimmerman is a graduate of Villanova University and the Lutheran Theological 
Southern Seminary. 
</P>
<P>
 Sunday worship services at the church are at 8:30 and 10 a.m. at 9812 Hamilton 
Ave. Information: (714) 962-5005. 
