<HEADLINE>
<P>
O.C. RELIGION NOTES / DAYE CLARK: CHURCH BUILDING TO BE DEDICATED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By DAYE CLARK 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The congregation of St. Elizabeth Ann Seton Church in Irvine will celebrate 
the dedication of its new church building with a special interfaith worship 
service Monday. 
</P>
<P>
 All are welcome to share in the evening of music, prayer and readings at 7:30 
at 9 Hillgate. Information: (714) 854-1000. 
</P>
</TEXT>
